#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" A top choice for floral needs. <br/>Elegant designs, excellent service, "
"and lasting beauty. \""
msgstr ""
"\" Et førsteklasses valg til blomsterbehov. <br/>Elegante designs, "
"fremragende service og varig skønhed. \""

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Exceptional flowers and service! <br/>They make every occasion special "
"and memorable. \""
msgstr ""
"\"Fantastiske blomster og service! <br/>De gør enhver lejlighed til noget "
"særligt og mindeværdigt.\""

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Their arrangements are stunning. Fresh, creative, and always beautifully "
"crafted. \""
msgstr ""
"\"Deres arrangementer er fantastiske. Friske, kreative og altid smukt "
"udformede.\""

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_framed_intro
msgid ""
"<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-lg btn-secondary o_translate_inline\">See the "
"Full Bloom</a>"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-lg btn-secondary o_translate_inline\">I fuldt "
"flor</a>"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_text_image
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Deliver flowers to live up to your dedication for your loved ones."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Vis din kærlighed med blomster til dem, der står dig nær."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<br/>Creating vibrant, handcrafted bouquets to celebrate every occasion.<br/"
"><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>Vi skaber livlige, håndlavede buketter til at fejre enhver "
"lejlighed.<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  Fresh "
"and beautiful"
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  Frisk og "
"smuk"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_title
msgid "A Deep Dive into Blooms and Beauty"
msgstr "Et dybdegående kig på blomster og skønhed"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"A delicate blend of soft pink roses and baby's breath, perfect for "
"expressing love and gratitude."
msgstr ""
"En delikat blanding af lyserøde roser og gypsophila – perfekt til at "
"udtrykke kærlighed og taknemmelighed."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_hexagonal
msgid "A place of paradise for flower lovers"
msgstr "Et paradis for blomsterelskere"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"A small shop with a very large selection of roses. Nice prices and above all "
"a very professional and friendly welcome."
msgstr ""
"En lille butik med et meget stort udvalg af roser. Gode priser og frem for "
"alt en meget professionel og venlig betjening."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"A wide range of high quality products and a warm welcome! I recommend this "
"shop 200%!"
msgstr ""
"Et stort udvalg af produkter af høj kvalitet og en hjertelig modtagelse! Jeg "
"kan anbefale denne butik 200 %!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_framed_intro
msgid "About Us"
msgstr "Om os"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline Turner, Bouquet Designer"
msgstr "Aline Turner, buketdesigner"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline is the mastermind behind our bespoke floral arrangements."
msgstr "Aline er hjernen bag vores skræddersyede blomsterarrangementer."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"As we use local growers, our flowers last longer and smell better. Just like "
"the event you want to celebrate with flowers!"
msgstr ""
"Da vi bruger lokale blomsteravlere, holder vores blomster længere og dufter "
"bedre. Ligesom den begivenhed, du ønsker at fejre med blomster!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid "Bio Flowers"
msgstr "Økologiske blomster"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_unveil
msgid "Bloom with Elegance"
msgstr "Elegant blomstring"

