msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_wavy_grid
msgid "Innovation and Design"
msgstr "Innovation og design"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Iris Joe, Customer Relations"
msgstr "Iris Joe, kunderelationer"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Iris ensures that each customer has a delightful experience."
msgstr "Iris sørger for, at hver enkelt kunde får en dejlig oplevelse."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_cards_grid
msgid ""
"Just as sunflowers always turn towards the sun, we are dedicated to "
"providing reliable service that meets your floral needs, every time."
msgstr ""
"Ligesom solsikker altid vender sig mod solen, bestræber vi os på altid at "
